      "description": "Comparison of shear stress transport and realizable k-epsilon turbulence closures for hemolysis scalar transport. SST k-omega selected based on superior near-wall resolution. Validation cases use correctly specified inlet velocity profiles derived from Doppler ultrasound measurements under controlled laboratory conditions."
