    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "Seven of thirteen credibility factors assessed and all meet or exceed required levels for MRL 2. Six factors not assessed are consistent with MRL 2 scoping. CFD model demonstrates sufficient credibility to support identification of worst-case hemolysis operating conditions for the Class II CPB device. RHI predictions agree with bench measurements within 8% across all operating points, satisfying the RH < 1 regulatory acceptance criterion. Assessment team concludes the model is fit for the stated context of use.",
